cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper addresses the problem of establishing correspondences between different instances of the same object using convolutional neural networks.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a neural network to directly regress the parameters of the transformation model.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel loss function based on cyclic consistency to solve the 2D point set registration problem.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with aligning images and finding geometric transformations.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper addresses the problem of matching semantic information in images.
